&lt;p&gt;Join Our Team at Clean Laundry - Part-Time Customer Service Attendant!&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Clean Laundry – 1030 Norwood Park Blvd. #320, Austin, TX 78753&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; $14.00–$15.00 per hour, depending on qualifications and experience&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Part-time, approximately 12–15 hours per week with 3–4 hour shifts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clean Laundry is seeking a dependable Part-Time Customer Service Attendant to help maintain a clean, safe, and welcoming environment for our customers. This role is ideal for someone who works well independently, likes a clear routine, and is looking for a reliable part-time opportunity with predictable hours and consistent work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Essential Duties:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete assigned cleaning and facility maintenance tasks each shift.&lt;/li&gt;
