&lt;li&gt;Provide courteous customer assistance as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What we&#39;re looking for:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable with a consistent attendance record.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work independently and manage assigned responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and ability to maintain a clean, organized facility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly and professional when interacting with customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Physical Requirements:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to&amp;nbsp;lift and carry up to 50 lbs occasionally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use step stools as needed to perform assigned duties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sit or stand for the majority of the shift.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frequent&amp;nbsp;bending, reaching, twisting, kneeling, squatting, pushing, and pulling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform repetitive tasks with hands and arms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Must be at least 18 years of age.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Employment is contingent upon the successful completion of a background check.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
