&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cleaning and Service Attendant - &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dubuque, IA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Love helping people of all ages? Enjoy keeping your surroundings clean and tidy? Then come join the Clean Laundry team as a Cleaning and Service Attendant at our Dubuque stores!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overall Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
