&lt;p&gt;Here are a few “must haves” each applicant should possess:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Great listening and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekday and weekend availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable transportation (Ability to travel between stores in the area)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to arrive on time, every time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested? Fill out your application now!&lt;/p&gt;
